summary: A clean up of the Karthspire area for the work-in-progress mod Reforging the Blades.
descriptionHtml:
It\'s all very over-grown and dirty so I just wanted to clean the place up and improve on the various areas.

Feel free to comment and leave your criticisms as I haven\'t got too much experience and there are a lot of things annoying me that I don\'t know how to change. My biggest problem is cleaning it up without leaving huge gaps.

Most of the objects I have simply deleted as opposed to disablng.
author: Drytor
